=== (1) V50 limit check [verified F3] ===
v_photon(k->0) = sqrt(1-eta^2/m2) = 0.9428 c  (V50: 0.9428c)
matter-branch c_eff^2 = 1+eta^2/m2 = 1.1111  (transverse pol. only)

=== (2) band scan K in [1.1,1.7] (photon-branch bath) ===
  K     W(K)    M2t     c0^2/e   n_tot/e   dm2/e^2(coh)
