band-avg: C_coh = dm2/e^2 = -0.01991 (coherent, K^-component only)
band-avg: n_tot/e = 0.04386, n_comp/e = 0.01462
Gaussian neutral-bath: dm2 = mu*n_comp^2 = -0.00884 e^2 (isotropic) [estimate]
single-mode neutral (F12c): -0.00996 e^2 + Floquet at (4K,4W)

=== (4) core mean-field slope ===
f0=0.6405, X=f0^2=0.4102, kappa*X^3=3.452 (>1/2: saturated => g'>0)
g'(X) = +2.2696   => d(omega^2)_core = g'(X)*n_comp = +0.03318 * e_bath

=== (5) PREDICTION TABLE: v67 bath ladder, ball omega=1.39 ===
dm2_amb = C_gauss*e^2 [estimate]; dm/m = dm2/(2 m2)
d_omega_core = g'*n_comp*e/(2 omega) [estimate, factor ~2 syst]
d_omega_amb  = dm2_amb/(2 omega)
 e_bath | n_comp   | dm2_amb    | dm_eff/m  | dw_core   | dw_amb     | dw_tot   | omega_pred
